<chapter id="chapter-introduction">
  <title>Introduction</title>

  <para>This plug-in contains a raster layer definition for accessing raster
  data from WMS servers. It has support for WMS versions (1.0.0, 1.1.0, 1.1.1
  and 1.3.0)</para>

  <para>Since version 1.8.0 of this plug-in, there is also built-in support
  for basic and digest HTTP authentication. On top of this, the option remains
  to add user name and password parameters as GET parameters to each WMS
  GetMap request.</para>
</chapter>
